of the good Lord,

00:19:00,724 --> 00:19:04,561
14 years of therapy
and two loving wives,

00:19:04,628 --> 00:19:07,097
I humbly believe

00:19:07,163 --> 00:19:09,332
I've made progress.

00:19:09,399 --> 00:19:11,935
But this story is not
about Izzy Delancy.

00:19:12,002 --> 00:19:15,906
