the point entirely.

00:19:33,557 --> 00:19:36,560
Cruelty is cruelty,

00:19:36,626 --> 00:19:39,029
whether the victim be a chicken

00:19:39,095 --> 00:19:41,464
or a malnourished African.

00:19:41,531 --> 00:19:43,833
