PSA targeting Mannleigh Chickens

00:19:58,582 --> 00:20:01,151
as the epitome
of everything that is wrong

00:20:01,218 --> 00:20:02,219
in the slaughter industry.

00:20:03,720 --> 00:20:07,691
It takes a manly man
to make a Mannleigh chicken.

00:20:07,757 --> 00:20:10,794
(rooster crowing)

00:20:10,860 --> 00:20:13,096
IZZY:
Now, perhaps you've purchased

00:20:13,163 --> 00:20:16,333
Mannleigh Roasters,
Fryers or Assorted Parts

00:20:16,399 --> 00:20:17,667
