00:32:05,137 --> 00:32:06,705
You're free to go.

00:32:15,948 --> 00:32:17,583
So was he right?

00:32:17,649 --> 00:32:19,151
Are we really just
picking on an old man

00:32:19,218 --> 00:32:21,220
or is he the bad guy?

00:32:23,222 --> 00:32:25,257
Well, he's associated
peripherally

00:32:25,324 --> 00:32:28,160
with all the victims,
and he certainly has
the right skills.

00:32:28,227 --> 00:32:30,662
Yeah... he spent
half his life

00:32:30,729 --> 00:32:33,265
in Locomotiveville.

00:32:33,332 --> 00:32:36,168
